Good then you should be freezing up so I don't have to worry about 
you. 

Megaton transforms to his T-Rex form to become a smaller target. he 
dropped beneath the missles. He landed with a crash which cracked the 
ice and left his footprints deeply imprinted in the ground. With a 
loud roar he turned his attention to Scyther. he breathed deeply once 
again firing abeam of ice at his opponent.
